---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="MoFA - Moxin Org">
  <div class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-fade-in">

      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">
        MoFA <br />
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-cyan to-blue-500">
          让普通开发者成为全栈 AI 工程师
        </span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light">
        一个旨在简化 AI 智能体开发的模块化框架。通过可组合、可扩展的架构构建、组合和部署智能代理。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 animate-fade-in relative z-10">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-cyan/10 to-blue-500/10 border border-accent-cyan/20 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all cursor-pointer text-center transform hover:scale-105" onclick="window.open('https://mofa.ai', '_blank')">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">访问 MoFA 网站</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse mb-4 text-lg">只需 6 分钟即可开始使用 MoFA 智能体框架。</p>
        <span class="text-accent-cyan font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          mofa.ai
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg>
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- MoFA Projects -->
    <section class="mb-24 animate-fade-in">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">MoFA 项目</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <a href="https://github.com/mofa-org/mofa" target="_blank" class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:border-accent-cyan/50 transition-all group cursor-pointer">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse group-hover:text-accent-cyan transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
            MoFA Framework
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path></svg>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse">为智能体开发提供基础的核心框架。具有可组合架构，允许通过 YAML 定义的流程连接智能体，内置 RAG（嵌入、分割、向量存储）、规划和工具集成模块。</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://mofa.ai" target="_blank" class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:border-accent-cyan/50 transition-all group cursor-pointer">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse group-hover:text-accent-cyan transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
            MoFA Stage
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path></svg>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse">用于 MoFA 开发的可视化 IDE。这个基于 Web 的平台包括可视化智能体管理、带 SSH 访问的集成 Web 终端、支持语法高亮的 Monaco 代码编辑器以及实时 WebSocket 通信。</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/mofa-org/mofa-studio" target="_blank" class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:border-accent-cyan/50 transition-all group cursor-pointer">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse group-hover:text-accent-cyan transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
            MoFA Studio
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path></svg>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse">用于本地构建和管理 MoFA 智能体的桌面应用程序。为智能体开发、测试和部署工作流提供直观的界面。</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Choose MoFA -->
    <section class="mb-24 animate-fade-in">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">为什么选择 MoFA</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">可组合智能体架构</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse">通过 YAML 定义的流程连接智能体，构建复杂的 AI 应用程序。利用包含 RAG、规划和工具集成模块的核心内核。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">快速智能体开发</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse">只需 6 分钟即可开始，支持快速设置和可视化 IDE。清晰的智能体开发结构大大减少了样板代码。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">丰富的智能体中心</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse">从 Agent Hub 访问 500+ 预构建的智能体，涵盖数据连接器、LLM 集成和专用工具。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">高度可扩展</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse">轻松编写自定义 Python 智能体。通过定义良好的接口集成第三方工具、模型和数据源。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-2">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">MoFA Stage IDE</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse mb-4">MoFA 的可视化管理平台 - 具有完整开发功能的基于 Web 的 IDE。</p>
          <ul class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-cyan rounded-full"></span>
              可视化智能体管理
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-cyan rounded-full"></span>
              带 SSH 的集成终端
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-cyan rounded-full"></span>
              Monaco 代码编辑器
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-cyan rounded-full"></span>
              实时 WebSocket
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-cyan rounded-full"></span>
              500+ 预构建智能体
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-cyan rounded-full"></span>
              语法高亮
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>



    <!-- Get Started -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="animate-fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">几秒钟内开始</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 flex items-center justify-center text-accent-cyan shrink-0 font-bold">
              1
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">安装 MoFA</h3>
              <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse">运行 pip 命令安装 MoFA 框架。</p>
              <code class="block mt-2 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/10 p-2 rounded text-sm text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10">pip install mofa</code>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 flex items-center justify-center text-accent-cyan shrink-0 font-bold">
              2
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">创建您的智能体</h3>
              <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse">使用我们的模板或从简单的 YAML 配置开始。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 flex items-center justify-center text-accent-cyan shrink-0 font-bold">
              3
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse">部署与扩展</h3>
              <p class="text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse">启动您的 AI 智能体并在不同环境中扩展它们。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative animate-slide-up">
        <div class="relative bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-2xl">
          <!-- Mock Flow Chart -->
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-8">
            <div class="bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 border border-accent-cyan text-accent-cyan px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-mono font-bold shadow-sm">
              Manager Agent
            </div>
            <div class="h-8 w-px bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-600"></div>
            <div class="flex gap-8">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/10 border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-mono text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse shadow-sm">
                  Researcher
                </div>
                <div class="text-xs text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse text-center max-w-[150px]">
                  Searches web for latest data
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/10 border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-mono text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse shadow-sm">
                  Writer
                </div>
                <div class="text-xs text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse text-center max-w-[150px]">
                  Drafts content based on research
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/10 border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-mono text-text-primary dark:text-text-inverse shadow-sm">
                  Critic
                </div>
                <div class="text-xs text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-inverse text-center max-w-[150px]">
                  Reviews and requests changes
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
